data.text:
Please take a moment to check the art of Matt Cullen, he does trojan work for the Irish Lung Fibrosis Association. Lung Fibrosis is a terminal illness he has been inflicted with for the last seven years and he donates a portion of proceeds to the ILFA. You can purchase his excellent works at reasonable prices through his site.

Matt Cullen
